WEBVTT

19:20.618 --> 19:23.245
That your boy
in the Monte Carlo?
Yeah, that's him.

19:24.747 --> 19:26.540
Yeah, he's got some skills.

19:27.208 --> 19:29.709
And he's crazy as hell,
I'm telling you.

19:30.753 --> 19:32.921
In a good way, though.
He's the man for the job.

19:38.261 --> 19:41.596
And he's got quite a record,
including three years upstate.

19:42.181 --> 19:44.099
Says here,
he's on house arrest now.

19:44.183 --> 19:46.768
Can't go more than
100 yards from his home.
